headline: Barclays Maintains Overweight on Intl Flavors & Fragrances, Raises Price Target to $91
summary: Barclays  analyst Lauren Lieberman   maintains Intl Flavors & Fragrances (NYSE:IFF) with a Overweight and raises the price target from $78 to $91.

headline: Mizuho Maintains Outperform on Intl Flavors & Fragrances, Raises Price Target to $92
